  "texts": [
    "In the testing stage, the model then experienced eight repetitions of four blocks of trials.",
    "In each block, one of the combinations of B+, R+, B-and R-was tested.",
    "The order of the four blocks was shuffled in each of the eight repetitions.",
    "In each block, the model first experi enced n ← {2, 4, 6} washout trials (equal numbers of B 0 and R 0 trials in a pseudorandom order).",
    "The model then experienced a triplet of trials, where the exposure trial was the combination (B+, R+, B-or R-) tested in a given block to assess singletrial learning of this combination."
  ],
